{"tid":1612210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"5紀律部隊發聯合聲明堅定支持特區政府及警隊止暴制亂","createTime":"2019-10-02T07:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:41:06.000Z","uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e034a74cd40f38c0cb9697da5e934472faa417","tid":1612210,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:35:19.000Z","msg":"入境處處長曾國衞、海關關長鄧以海、消防處處長李建日、懲教署署長胡英明，及政府飛行服務隊總監胡偉雄，發表聯合聲明，表示全力支持警隊嚴厲執法，堅定支持特區政府及警隊止暴制亂。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說，近期香港發生的連串暴力行為，不斷升級，接連發生毆鬥、縱火、襲警、投擲汽油彈，以至攻擊港鐵設施、政府建築物及侮辱國旗等各種嚴重暴行，遠超任何容忍尺度，嚴重威脅市民安全，整個社會都受到極其嚴峻的挑戰，各紀律部隊必須予以最嚴厲譴責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483766-20191002.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483766-20191002.htm&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=3f78bc50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483766-20191002.htm&h=c10088e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483766-20191002.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e2f1679b2d8c605e05404d7ab37a25bfbb4d4b14","tid":1612210,"uid":163797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"急不及待想上制裁名單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cddf410f2627f58fd6a0094db0ec9493b3cd51","tid":1612210,"uid":123552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"769f0f61fe2cb56dbdd354b87a631011847ca60f","tid":1612210,"uid":197149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:38:32.000Z","msg":"算啦佢地係政府部門，都無希望佢地企係雞蛋呢邊啦"},{"pid":"78f71f4e58d4c8103b42a8c1a9457748adfee5e9","tid":1612210,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:41:06.000Z","msg":"3司12局都係由中央委任<br />\n向中央負責<br />\n明白未！？"}]}